Type of Feat: General
Prerequisite: Casting 1st level spells.
Specifics: A character with this feat is more adept in spell casting based on the time of day, gaining a +2 bonus to spell save DC for all spells cast during the day and -2 for all spells cast at night, during the dawn and dusk periods this becomes a -1.
Use: Automatic. This feat might be selected multiple times, but the effects cancel each other and result in no effect at all.